*Maybelline New York Cosmetics https://www.maybelline.com/
-Instant Anti-Age ERASER Multi-Use Concealer (00 Ivory)
-SUPER STAY 24h Full Coverage Foundation (10 Ivory)
*Essence Cosmetics https://essencemakeup.com/
-MySkin Perfector Tinted Primer (10 Light Beige)
*Revolution Beauty https://www.revolutionbeauty.com/
-‘Conceal & Define’ Full Coverage Concealer (C9)

*Il Makiage https://ilmakiage.com
-Mineral Baked Bronzer (Waka Waka)
*Rimmel London https://www.rimmellondon.com/en-gb
-Natural Bronzer (027 Sun Dance)
*Jybel MUA https://jybelmua.com/
-Loose Setting Powder (Translucent)**

👑 BLUSH & HIGHLIGHTER: 
*BPerfect Cosmetics https://www.bperfectcosmetics.com/
-The Dimension Collection | Polar Vortex Highlight (Snow Angel)
-The Dimension Collection | Scorched Blusher (Magma)

👑 EYEBROWS & EYELINER:
*Anastasia Beverly Hills https://www.anastasiabeverlyhills.com/
-DipBrow Pomade (Blonde & Medium Brown)
-Brow Powder Duo (Soft Brown)
*Inglot Cosmetics https://inglotcosmetics.com/
- AMC Gel Eyeliner (77 black)
-Duraline Makeup Mixing Liquid
*Davis https://www.aliexpress.com/
-’Waterproof Protection’ Lip & Eye Liner Pencil (Color 1 & 13)
*BeautyCare Israel https://www.beautycare.co.il/
-Super Resistant Gel Eyeliner (02 Royal Blue)

👑 LASHES & MASCARA:
*Essence Cosmetics https://essencemakeup.com/
-‘Bye Bye Panda Eyes!’ Smudge-Proof Volumizing & Defining Mascara (01 Black)
*Ali Express https://www.aliexpress.com/
-Lash Book
*Ardell https://www.ardellshop.com/
-DUO Striplash Adhesive (Black or Clear)

👑 EYESHADOW & EYE PRIMER:
*Natasha Denona https://www.natashadenona.com/
-Eyeshadow Base (01 light/beige)
*Madaj Beauty London https://madajbeautylondon.com/
-‘The Witching Hour Collection’ Eye Perfect Glitter Eyeshadow (Morticia)**
-‘The Witching Hour Collection’ Eye Perfect Glitter Eyeshadow (Sabrina)**  
-‘The Witching Hour Collection’ Eye Perfect Matte Eyeshadow (Winifred)** 
-‘The Witching Hour Collection’ Eye Perfect Matte Eyeshadow (Marie)** 
*Frikin Fabulous Cosmetics https://www.etsy.com/shop/Stickerdollzlashes
-Duochrome Single Eyeshadow (Sultan)**

👑 LIPS:
*Madaj Beauty London https://madajbeautylondon.com/
-‘The Witching Hour Collection’ Lip Plumper (Venom)** 
-Sakura Shine Lipstick (Tsubaki)**
*Davis https://www.aliexpress.com/
-‘Wood Lipliner Pencil’ (06)
